      "content": "i know i should probably see someone but it's 2am and i cant drive right now. i just need to know if it is actually dangerous to just take another dose or if that's just what they tell everyone. like if i just take 400mg more of the ibuprofen, is that really going to hurt me? maybe it's fine just this once to get through the night.",
